title: Papa's Cookies Shop v1.2 (unlimited coins in the shop)
description:
Serve Customers ASAP! This is an awesome Cookie Shop Arcade-Style Game. Create & Serve Dozens of Delicious & Unique Cookies out of Your Own Cookie Shop. 
Decorate and Update your Shop as you like. 

------------------------------------------------------ 

Here's the scoop, your shop is waiting and it's time to make some fantastic cookies to serve to your customers! Arcade-style game will keep you on your toes, timing you as you make different kinds of cookies and serve your customers quickly. Make sure you get the order right!

Required Android O/S : 2.2+
